data.description: Great home is a quiet area close to everything in Prescott.  Minutes from Yavapai Community Hospital and tons of shopping. Home is being painted inside and out. Large fenced in rear yard, mature trees, stucco and stone exterior. Home is perfect for folks who need lots of rooms and has been an excellent rental property as well. No HOA is an added bonus with the great home. Roof, HVAC system, water heater all replaced 12 years ago. 2 water heaters for this home. Extra large laundry room with tons of storage space.
